Spring Template : Localisation
==============================

o Introduction
o Running the template
o More info

Introduction
------------
This is a Spring template for localising a web application
at the URL level. e.g.
http://localhost:8080/spring-template/en/
It contains English (UK) and Scottish Gaelic versions:
http://localhost:8080/spring-template/en/
http://localhost:8080/spring-template/gd/

Running the template
--------------------
You can see the template in action by running Jetty:
mvn jetty:run
and pointing your browser to:
http://localhost:8080/spring-template

More info
